{"tid":521491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"埃及樂蜀熱氣球墮地一死","createTime":"2018-01-06T15:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T15:15:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdf4f244e5e920fa629d8746996deb3619db8aa","tid":521491,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180106/20266184?_ga=2.51060586.2139109552.1514873408-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F20266184%3F_ga%3D2.51060586.2139109552.1514873408-581282530.1504247435&d=p%2BsVDQEEkqe1gYArcpEg2Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f7bf0b57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F20266184%3F_ga%3D2.51060586.2139109552.1514873408-581282530.1504247435&h=d4637aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180106/20266184?_ga=2.51060586.2139109552.1514873408-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n埃及樂蜀熱氣球墮地一死<br />\n<br />\n4,872<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n <br />\n埃及南部旅遊城市樂蜀（Luxor，圖）昨日發生觀光熱氣球墮地事故，官方通訊社指1人死亡，據報是34歲南非男遊客，另外14人傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180106/large/16860043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F16860043.jpg&h=f3c6898b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n載20人　遇強風失控<br />\n<br />\n中東通訊社（MENA）報道，事件共造成1死14傷，兩名傷者情況嚴重。埃及衞生部指死者是34歲男性，另有官員指他是南非人。新華社引述官員報道，傷者分別來自澳洲、法國、南非及阿根廷。<br />\n<br />\n當地官員指，肇事熱氣球日出前起飛，約45分鐘後、飛行至450米高時遇上強風，失控墜落山區，當時載有包括外國遊客在內共20人。氣象部門同日較早前發出強風警告。樂蜀過往多次發生熱氣球意外，死傷最嚴重的發生在2013年2月，熱氣球起火墜毀造成19名外國遊客死亡，包括9名港人。2016年亦有熱氣球緊急降落，導致22名中國遊客輕傷，其後埃及政府規定熱氣球飛行高度不可超過2,000米。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社/《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n築地「日本一」251萬成交<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n朱克伯格冀修正fb保安　防濫用"},{"pid":"b81b4a2fe22305935fac740e9297a9d8a2c28b77","tid":521491,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"又跌一次,  前幾年先跌過一次  好似死咗唔知幾多個香港遊客."},{"pid":"4c00261f48bd8815dc2885a54def5989722f8ed6","tid":521491,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔係支那人"}]}